data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_ed03de879aca549e0069988f95b6c48190a3082a6b2f246fc3","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":368,"text":"The available Contoso documentation in this workspace currently describes one product in detail: **SmartView Glasses** by **Contoso Galaxy Innovations**, in the **Smart Eyewear** category .\n\n## Contoso SmartView Glasses — features\nSmartView Glasses are positioned as smart eyewear with a strong focus on AR + hands-free interaction :\n\n- **Augmented Reality (AR) interface**: Provides an AR experience delivered through the glasses .  \n- **Voice-controlled AI agent**: Built-in voice control for interacting with an AI assistant hands-free .  \n- **HD video recording with 3D audio**: Capture high-definition video while also recording spatial/3D audio .  \n- **UV protection and blue light filtering**: Designed to protect eyes from UV and reduce blue light exposure .  \n- **Wireless charging with extended battery life**: Supports wireless charging and emphasizes longer usage time between charges .\n\n## What the documentation includes (beyond features)\nThe same document also outlines what you’d expect in official product documentation :\n\n- **User Guide sections** covering introduction, overview, sizing/fit, care/maintenance, break-in period, safety tips, and troubleshooting .  \n- **Warranty**: Two-year limited warranty on electronic components .  \n- **Support contact**: support@contoso-galaxy-innovations.com .  \n- **Returns**: 30-day return policy .  \n- **FAQ topics** like syncing with devices, connection troubleshooting, and AR environment customization .\n\nIf you expect more Contoso products to be included, upload or point me to the additional product docs and I’ll summarize each product and compare their features side-by-side."}

